{"tid":1496770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 中環被大陸化","createTime":"2019-08-22T16:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T16:42:36.000Z","uid":306833,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"644bb9ed277be8ad1215db14d893c8dfe6c52dba","tid":1496770,"uid":306833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜去中環碼頭都未係變成咁<br />\n今日經過就見到無啦啦多左勁多大陸落黎嘅大媽係度賣唱<br />\n數埋數埋都有成十幾檔<br />\n檔檔都有哂打燈音響腳架觀眾席咁<br />\n裝備齊到似係有人吹雞落黎搵食咁<br />\n<br />\n啲大媽著住又娘又窄身嘅摟屌裙<br />\n又唱埋哂啲50年代嘅歌又跳埋舞咁<br />\n有廣東話普通話閩南話都有<br />\n吸引左一堆呀伯坐滿觀眾席<br />\n啲呀伯又會不時比啲野飲同錢比啲大媽<br />\n呢個畫面加埋啲噪音污染<br />\n唔講仲以為自己去左深洲呀大陸啲廣場咁<br />\n係正CBD擺檔  真係影響市容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有圖有真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QuCdnKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuCdnKg.jpg&h=a656d1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvtLYhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnvtLYhD.jpg&h=fc9abea2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42d089a42957fd6b4882b6b485727b27c0e1c9e6","tid":1496770,"uid":175976,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"有咩能力改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66051745f97da39296806211853a49b4b7c5fdc3","tid":1496770,"uid":271049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:13:56.000Z","msg":"返工時間中環啲寫字樓同街道聽到普通話多過英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申中環返工"},{"pid":"735c77c799557f6ded3fbac66a58bafd3295be71","tid":1496770,"uid":246175,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"癡線 我今日都經過開 印象中既中環碼頭唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s